REMARK 300 REMARK: THIS CRYSTAL FORM CONTAINS TWO DIMERS IN THE ASYMMETRIC      
REMARK 300 UNIT.  EACH MONOMER CONSISTS OF TWO SEPARATE POLYPEPTIDE             
REMARK 300 CHAINS, ALPHA AND BETA, ONE CA++ AND ONE MN++ ION, AND THE           
REMARK 300 MURAMYL-DIPEPTIDE.  THE ALPHA CHAIN CONSISTS OF 181                  
REMARK 300 RESIDUES AND THE BETA CHAIN CONSISTS OF 52 RESIDUES.                 
REMARK 300 MONOMER 1 CONTAINS ALPHA CHAIN *A*, BETA CHAIN *B*,                  
REMARK 300 MURAMYL-DIPEPTIDE *1*, CA 228, AND MN 229.  MONOMER 2                
REMARK 300 CONTAINS ALPHA CHAIN *C*, BETA CHAIN *D* AND MURAMYL-                
REMARK 300 DIPEPTIDE *2*.  MONOMERS 3 AND 4 ARE LABELLED SIMILARLY,             
REMARK 300 WITH CHAIN IDENTIFIERS *E*, *F*, *3*, *G*, *H* AND *4*.              
REMARK 300 EACH DIMER HAS TWO MONOMERS WHICH ARE RELATED BY A                   
REMARK 300 NON-CRYSTALLOGRAPHIC TWO-FOLD AXIS.                                  
